gmd:description.gco:CharacterString: IGS personnel received an ESRI shapefile named "DAMS_DNR_WATER_IN_100331.SHP" from IDNR personnel (Mike Martin) on April 21, 2010. "DAMS_DNR_WATER_IN_100331.SHP" was loaded into ESRI ArcMap 9.3.1 and the data were examined for completeness. The shapefile was then renamed to DAMS_IDNR_IN.SHP to conform to IGS naming conventions.

This metadata file was pre-parsed and parsed using CNS (Chew and Spit, v. 2.6.1) and MP (Metadata Parser, v. 2.7.1) software written by Peter N. Schweitzer (U.S. Geological Survey). The errors generated by MP were all addressed and corrected, except that no values were assigned to "Abscissa_Resolution" and "Ordinate_Resolution."
